Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 肚子饿了 肚子饿了 肚子饿了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快叫外卖来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,您今天摄入的卡路里已经超标了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,面装在另一个肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,面和米饭都是卡路里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了 你就给他叫份外卖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她两小时前刚吃过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不对啦 言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?怪我咯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这里要这样 然后这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(640,659)}面~面~面~可爱的面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(640,659)}啊~好想见「面」啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 一 二 三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(682.857,720.476)}eins     zwei   drei
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这里 注意脚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,别O型腿 别说德语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(640,659)}I love 面 ~ 面 ~ 面 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(640,659)}超喜欢面 ~ 最最喜欢面了 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(640,659)}酱油 ~ 醋 ~ 和味增 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(641.6,654.457)}结束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚刚看完德国周刊杂志 顺嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快点干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,面 ~ 面 ~ 面 ~ 可爱的面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多点行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:00:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,言叶 蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是规定了只有午休时间可以玩游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们太懒散了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让你们重新绷紧神经
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,明天事务所大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,明天不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐要出差去参加这里的会议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去购物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,面 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.82,SPE,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.28,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}やあ また会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:36.65,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ねぇ こんばんは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.57,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}いや こんにちはだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:41.12,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}広いようで 狭いようで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.83,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}退屈はいらないみたいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.71,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}あぁ 問題は依然あって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:48.75,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}頭痛いんだけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:51.17,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}少しずつって言い聞かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:54.34,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}願い事叶えて行きましょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:04.22,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}拾い集めた後悔のかけらたちを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.48,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}夜が明ける前に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:10.48,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}何遍を貼って 並べてて 希望に変える
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.02,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}10秒継続中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:17.03,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}桜が去つて散ったその後で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:20.82,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}何が真実なのかは かるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:24.66,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}future melody そう今は奏でて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:29.58,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}愛が世界救うのだなんて 僕は信じてないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:35.25,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}今 目の前の君が 明日を生きれるくらいには
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:36.55,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ありえない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:39.05,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不条理は吹き飛ばしていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.34,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}with 喜怒哀楽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.81,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}大丈夫さ　どこまでもゆくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:28.19,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalalalalalala
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:32.90,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalalalalala
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.28,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}呀啊 又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:36.65,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}呐 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.57,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不 应该是中午好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:41.12,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}好像很宽敞 又好像很拥挤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.83,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不过貌似和「无聊」二字无缘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.71,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}啊 问题依然还在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:48.75,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}真是让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:51.17,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不过还是向我慢慢道来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:54.34,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}让我们一起去实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:58.38,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}I shall remember I wanna do I shall remember
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:04.22,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}将散落一地的后悔的碎片小心收起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.48,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在天明之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:10.48,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}一遍遍地粘合 一遍遍地重排 将之变为希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.02,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}持续10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:17.03,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在那满树樱花逝去之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:20.82,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}什么才是真实 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:24.66,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}future melody 没错 现在就奏响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:29.58,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}都说爱会拯救世界 我可一点都不信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:35.25,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}现在 眼前的你 想要享受明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:36.55,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:39.05,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}先把不合理统统打飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.34,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}with 喜怒哀乐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.81,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}放心吧 我们无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:49.27,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalala　lalalalalala!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:53.82,SPE,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:56.03,SPE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\fs50\pos(1042,674)}第二天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还是我一个人搞定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是我太嫩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天早上扫除完…上午去了那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,元老院那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因为樱花祭的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,被臭骂一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,说要我继承职责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真是够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我去做点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你是吃完再走吧 恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得还有鱼肉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 别勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,等等嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,给 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…一如既往的好厨艺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,太鲜美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,粗茶淡饭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有那烦人三人组在 好清静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 寂寞了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,桃…桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧 桃华你的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不小心又暴走了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,反正下周前能痊愈的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,枷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,本来是带着的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会控制自己的力量 别随便出门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有我跟着呢 你有什么意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小 ~ 恭 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,当哥哥的平时嘴里不饶人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但忏悔日的时候 句句都不离桃华呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 今天听说只有哥哥和秋名在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然手艺不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是做了牛肉盖饭来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看来多余了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我要 谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,放凉了 就更难吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 我也去吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?你还没吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 早点说不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,难得来一趟 大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我再去添个菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,秋…秋名亲手做的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,口水…口水…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了呢 能吃到心仪的人做的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,讨…讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,八重你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为这个我才不让你出门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你带着枷都不能完全控制力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 总之先收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我…我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,省省吧 你给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,桃华 我来送你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小恭 你说的太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,槙春爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这种力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥一脸失落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,被秋名甩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,太…太直接了啊 水奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧 幼儿园放学了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,狮堂先生没来接吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙太慢了 我们自己回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,呀吼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,才晚了一小会儿就自己回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不行…刹车也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,水奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,桃华 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,叫救护车 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要这种力量了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你如果有继承职责
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,桃华也不会遇到这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们哪有这么容易挂掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在小看我们吸血鬼吗 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛嘛…总之是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说到底这全都怪你吧 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,记得好好保养车子啊 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…突然方向盘和刹车都失灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名和恭助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在哦 他们在等候室里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好像总算冷静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,气消了没?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪你没继承自己的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,害多少妖怪不能自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了 病人都没法睡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别再说了 恭助君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小恭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,把舌头也剪掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧 桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,之后拜托咯 茱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是好久没见他俩吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说基本上都是为了桃华的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 狮堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,职责是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还没听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多该让你们知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这个城市里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,住着很多妖怪对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,想过是为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪聚集到这里都只为了一个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,目的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大家为了比泉家的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让他们把自己送回原本应该居住的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,才来到了这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:11:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,其实妖怪这种生物 原本是生存在另一个次元的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个次元?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 不管哪个次元 其实都是同一个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哈? 什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 假设同一个世界住着次元不同的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不同的次元之间是无法相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因为双方次元不同 所以认识不到对方的存在而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不是说 现在这里可能还有别人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我们虽然是妖怪 却生活在这边的世界里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们这些生活在这边世界的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是背离了世界之理的异端
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,异端?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,本来妖怪是不会老也不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在却会老去 也会死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为力量不安定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们去那边世界岂不是更好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人去了之后还能再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的世界是否真的适合妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候我也总是受欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后被哥哥背回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不准欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不记得有过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 哥哥小时候也没什么朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只有秋名不怕你 总是陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上只是打架而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 你有想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,背负着责任的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我们要怎么才能去那边的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就要说说「职责」了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,打个比方 换广播频道的时候要这样调整对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是在次元间移动的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样 将生活在这个世界的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,参照那边世界的次元「调律」一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是职责的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好像懂了有好像没懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那么提问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那边世界的广播局在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没有基准的话是无法调律的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以需要一个同时存在于这边世界和那边世界的参照物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,参照物?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西同时也是这城市的名胜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,知道是什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,名胜?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,跨越两个次元存在的七棵灵樱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,「七乡」沉睡的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是樱新町
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,将妖怪送回原次元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是比泉家家主——秋名继承的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,调律之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,槙春 不能再给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对市里的各位还有阿姬也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬还没醒 没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那孩子会哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她肯定不会让我走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,原理我大概是懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但究竟是什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,具体会发生什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,从这边的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,消失得无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 比泉家的家主们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,把这一职责与「杀人」…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,视作同一种行径
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓活着 便是与他人交流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在不断地交流之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,「活着的证明」开始逐渐成型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,待它消灭之时 也就意味着「死」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我再问你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你有杀人的觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥要说绝不能说的事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,胖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,过分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别…别…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才打得我好惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,已经忘记我小时候整天欺负你的那份恩情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那算什么恩情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你也没少还手好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧 这个不是恩而是仇…那他岂不没说错…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,况且如果你有继承职责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我就能和桃华在那边世界幸福的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是我们 其他妖怪也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,桃华桃华的…你这妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,话说我没有继承职责...是谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可你从来没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那要不要我在这调律一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就把她送回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我很冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我等等就乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,听话?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,首先把枷摘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这…摘掉的话力量会解放的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,给我快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,摘掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那么接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,出全力揍我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?还是一如既往地搞不懂你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你从小就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大家明明都怕我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你跟没事人似的过来找茬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这次又让我出全力揍你?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别胡扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真这么做的话 你那副人类身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,少罗嗦 快来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说怕我还手?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你这妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…喂…喂 秋名 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不…你的样子看起来很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我说完全不痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你的力量根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不值得我调律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这种程度的力量而已 我会有办法对付的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你当我开事务所是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有一天我对付不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那时…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那时我再亲手给你打到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是把我们送走的话 不是比保护到底更轻松些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 我啊 不想与这城市里任何一个妖怪分别
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,任何一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 我们的町长也不会让你们走的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你嘴上这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,其实只是不想和桃华分开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我决不允许她和你交往
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过是全员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以也包括你啊 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,爽快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…竟然拿调律桃华作威胁 实在不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,万一出了事故 你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那时请务必负起责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?桃华?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,喔?你把桃华迷得不轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕…比刚才还可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,问题解决
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,打一架就能和解 男人真难懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是更喜欢拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,阿嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬 你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 他俩又搞这套?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,男孩子就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,关系好到会打架
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是恋人间的准则吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,和恋人差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那俩人关系很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要多留心自己的车子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要被小偷轻易操纵了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想被母狐狸说教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 知道那家伙继承了职责也算不亏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可别断了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,比泉家的血脉
